<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رواه البخاري <span class="c2">(٢ / ٢٦٤ - ٢٦٥)</span> ومسلم <span class="c2">(٢ / ٩٥)</span> وأبو داود <span class="c2">(١ / ٢٣٦)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
